  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Digivolving] You may trash up to 3 blue cards from
    your hand. For each card trashed by this effect, you may trash 1 card under 1
    of your opponent's Digimon or Tamers. Then, 1 of your opponent's Digimon or Tamers
    without cards under it can't suspend until the end of your opponent's turn.[Opponent's
    Turn] [Once Per Turn] When an opponent's Digimon attacks, end that attack by
    returning 3 cards with [Jellymon]\_in their text from your trash to the bottom
    of your deck."
